skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: counting sheep
des:
Counting sheep is a mental exercise used in many cultures as a means of putting oneself to sleep. The Counting Sheep skill helps you to fall asleep by counting up 200 sheep. 
If necessary, you can restart the counting easily.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
